{"tid":1351502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[溫故知新]記唔記得邊個周永勤2017。⋯","createTime":"2019-07-22T15:36:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T16:10:53.000Z","uid":103230,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e42cc8a921ad5d3473e2344e5bdc018d831e6edf","tid":1351502,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:36:12.000Z","msg":"去年參選立法會的元朗區議員周永勤，聲稱受到威脅而被迫棄選，引發輿論嘩然。事件後他專注地區工作，已甚少就敏感政治議題發聲。不過今日他就用個人Facebook帳號選擇「出席」一個網上聯署，要求香港律師會對立法會議員何君堯展開紀律調查。<br />\n<br />\n由團體「匯政衞言」發起的網上聯署，質疑何君堯「殺無赦」言論違反《律師執業規則》，嚴重損害香港執業律師的專業形象，對香港法律界的形象造成強烈衝擊，因此要求律師會對何君堯展開專業操守的聆訊及調查，以維護香港法律界人士的專業地位。<br />\n<br />\n本網記者發現，今日早上周永勤在聯署的活動專頁上，選擇了「Going（出席）」的選項。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/tag/周永勤/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Ftag%2F%E5%91%A8%E6%B0%B8%E5%8B%A4%2F&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn24429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=11ff66f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Ftag%2F%E5%91%A8%E6%B0%B8%E5%8B%A4%2F&h=2a9bc179\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/tag/周永勤/</a>"},{"pid":"e71de97732aad996ab74057d2372eeb8909efa7c","tid":1351502,"uid":231124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:36:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1351394/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1351394/page/1</a><br />\n[長期置頂/集思廣益]727 元朗地勢分析/討論<br />\n入黎討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95e49cefe65a67940daee02070335edba817607a","tid":1351502,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:39:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/m5AwOkHFRJ8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fm5AwOkHFRJ8&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn24429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=a11006a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/m5AwOkHFRJ8</a>"},{"pid":"caeb3d7d0ce53262d7f61ebf6b590a546aea01fc","tid":1351502,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislik